
/Battles
    Post
        Make chat. Req user_id of initiating trainer.
        Generates Battle_id format 20241231-12 where 12 is the 12th battle of the day.
    GET
        Get details of all active battles.
        {Battle_Id, Initiating Trainer id, target_id (be it wild, trainer, or None)},
    /<Battle_Id>
        GET
            get details of current battle

